9. Risks, Dependencies & Assumptions
ServiceNow read-only API role will be granted (request already in progress).
Rate limits: Table API is generous; monitor X-RateLimit headers.
CMDB data quality in ServiceNow assumed reasonable.
No real-time requirement (polling is acceptable).
Dependencies
ServiceNow team to approve OAuth client + grant roles.
Network firewall rules (OCP → ServiceNow).
